## Add password to pdf

-> sudo apt install qpdf  
 
-> qpdf --encrypt <user_password> <owner_password> 256 -- <input_file>.pdf <output_protected>.pdf

<user_password>: The password required for someone to view the file.
<owner_password>: The password required to change the PDF's security settings later.
256: Specifies the encryption strength (AES-256). 









